---
title: Sticky Sesame Sweet Potato Tacos with Mushrooms, Pickled Cucumbers, Creamy Sriracha Sauce & Fried Onions
description: If you, like us, can’t get through the week without at least one taco night, we’ve got you. Here, our chefs put together a sweet and savory veggie taco that’s sure to satisfy. There’s sweet potato and mushrooms glazed with tangy hoisin, tender bell pepper, crunchy pickled cucumbers, sesame seeds, and creamy Sriracha sauce, all piled into steamy-soft tortillas. Get ready for a totally spec-taco-lar meal.
